A rare release by Willam. It was available only by directly purchasing through his website upon release with a limited amount of copies made. It has since never gone back on sale or been reprinted, nor has he made it available on any streaming service. Some of the songs have been removed as standalone tracks from iTunes, Spotify, and SoundCloud (where previously available) so it's impossible to compile a version of the album through the standalone single releases. I have yet to find a lossless rip myself so for now I'm just uploading what I have (320kbps MP3 CDRip).
